### Create New Account
POST http://localhost:1337/balance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user123",
  "amount": 1000
}

### Get Balance
GET http://localhost:1337/balance?user_id=user123

### Add Amount
POST http://localhost:1337/balance/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user123",
  "amount": 500
}

### Deduct Amount
POST http://localhost:1337/balance/deduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user123",
  "amount": 200
}

### Get Balance Again
GET http://localhost:1337/balance?user_id=user123
